quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  16,73,"Uye vanonamata vamwe kunze kwaAllah seizvo zvisingapi raramo ipi zvayo kwavari kubva kumatenga nepasi, uye hazvikwanisi"
  16,74,"Saka musava munoisa mberi mienzaniso naAllah. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoziva uye imi hamuzivi"
  16,75,"Allah vanoisa mberi muenzaniso wemuranda (asingatendi) ari pasi peumwe munhu, haana simba rezvese, uye nemurume (mutendi) uyo watakapa raramo yakanaka kubva kwatiri uye anoishandisa muchivande uye nepachena. Vakaenzana here? Kurumbidzwa kwese nekutenda ndekwa Allah. Asi vakawanda vavo havazivi"
  16,76,"Uye Allah vanopa muenzaniso wevarume vaviri, mumwe chete wavo chimumumu (asingatendi), haana simba pane zvese, uye mutoro kune mukuru wake; zvese zvaanomutuma, haauyi nezvakanaka. Akaenzana here neuyo (mutendi) anoraira zvakafanira, uye ari pagwara rakatwasuka"
  16,77,"Uye Allah ndivo muridzi wezvese zvisingaoneki zviri mumatenga nepasi. Uye nyaya yenguva (zuva rekutongwa) yakafanana nekubwaira kweziso, kana kuti iri pedyo. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vane simba pamusoro pezvese"
  16,78,"Uye Allah vakakuburitsai kubva munhumbu dzana amai venyu musingazivi kana chii zvacho, uye vakakupai nzeve, maziso nemoyo kuti zvimwe mungatende"
  16,79,"Havaoni here shiri dzichibhururuka mumhepo? Hapana anodzikata kunze kwaAllah. Zvirokwazvo, mune izvi mune zviratidzo kune avo vanotenda (muhumwechete hwaAllah)"